Tokyo Stocks Lower at Midday
</SUBHEAD>
<P>
   TOKYO (AP) -- Tokyo stocks fell Tuesday morning on profit-taking as investors
locked in profits after the previous day's gains. The Nikkei shed 96.81 points
to 15,905.90 at the end of the morning session.
</P>
