tying ninth-inning rally, and Dante Bichette singled home the winning run in the
10th as the Reds beat the Atlanta Braves 3-2 Monday night. Jones' poor throw to
first let Cincinnati come back for only its fifth victory in 30 games against
the Braves since 1997.
AP NewsBrief by VINCENT K. WILLIS 
</P>
