Coracao said. ''They didn't try to calm people down.''
</P>
<P>
   The Daily Publico newspaper claimed lead singer Liam Gallagher
lost his temper because the crowd would not join in singing.
</P>
<P>
   ''Due to Liam's tantrum, the hostility of a small section of the
audience spread and became general contempt,'' the newspaper's
critic wrote.
