<P>
   LOS ANGELES (AP) -- ''Friends'' actress Jennifer Aniston is no
friend of Celebrity Skin magazine.
</P>
<P>
   Aniston sued the magazine's publishers Monday for printing
photographs of her sunbathing topless in her back yard. The lawsuit
claims the magazine violated Aniston's right to privacy.
</P>
<P>
   Aniston, 31, and ''Friends'' co-stars Courteney Cox and Lisa
Kudrow were featured on the magazine cover. The headline read
''First Time Photos -- Friends Stars X-Posed.''
</P>
<P>
