Publishing Group claims that a ''stalkerazzi'' snapped the photos
of her after climbing a neighbor's fence.
</P>
<P>
   Aniston, who married actor Brad Pitt on July 29, seeks
unspecified damages and wants a judge to order the publisher to
stop distributing the pictures.
</P>
