<HEADLINE> Profiles of FirstEnergy Corp. and GPU Inc.  </HEADLINE>
By The Associated Press	   A look at FirstEnergy Corp. and GPU Inc.:
FirstEnergy Corp.
<TEXT>
<P>
   Headquarters - Akron, Ohio.
</P>
<P>
   Service area - Ohio and Pennsylvania.
</P>
<P>
   Chairman - Peter Burg, 54.
</P>
<P>
   Operating subsidiaries - Ohio Edison, Toledo Edison, Cleveland
Electric Illuminating, Pennsylvania Power.
</P>
<P>
   Financial - Revenue was $6.3 billion, net income $568.3 million,
$2.50 per share, during 1999.
GPU Inc.
</P>
<P>
   Headquarters: Morristown, N.J.
</P>
<P>
   Service area - New Jersey, Pennsylvania and internationally in
England, Argentina and Australia.
</P>
<P>
   Chairman - Fred D. Hafer, 59.
</P>
<P>
   Operating subsidiaries - Jersey Central Power &AMP; Light,
Metropolitan Edison and Pennsylvania Electric. GPU Capital and GPU
Electric and their subsidiaries own, operate and fund the
acquisition of electric and gas transmission and distribution
systems in foreign countries. GPU International and GPU Power and
their subsidiaries develop, own and operate generation facilities
in the United States and foreign countries.
</P>
<P>
   Financial - Revenue was $4.7 billion, net income $459 million,
$3.66 per share, during 1999.
</P>
